<figureCitation id="98F21AC48EF1FF7F489053AAFEA8FB6E" box="[160,269,1158,1182]" captionStart="PLATE 51" captionStartId="192.[151,233,1880,1903]" captionTargetBox="[188,1409,218,1832]" captionTargetId="figure-82@192.[166,1421,195,1858]" captionText="PLATE 51. Chelae, holotypes. A. Anteon yasumatsui (from Olmi 1984). B. A. malaysianum (=A. yasumatsui) (from Olmi 1987c). C. A. yoshimotoi (from Olmi 1991). D. A. yunnanense (from Xu et al. 2006b). E. A. zhangae (from Xu et al. 2010a). Scale bar 0.14 mm for A and B, 0.18 mm for C, 0.15 mm for D and 0.16 mm for E." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5278548" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5278548/files/figure.png" pageId="191" pageNumber="192">Plate 51C</figureCitation>
